al-nasb-lineage","tag-monotheism-tawhid","tag-surah-al-ikhlaas"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-8Fd","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":34320,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/07\/20\/surat-al-ikhlaas-jannah-obligatory\/","url_meta":{"origin":33307,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Quran: Surat al-Ikhlas makes Paradise obligatory","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 20, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: I met with the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and he heard a man reciting the verses, \u201cSay: He is Allah, the One, the Eternal Refuge,\u201d (112:1-2). The Prophet said, \u201cIt is necessary for him.\u201d I said, \u201cWhat is necessary?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cParadise.\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34322,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/07\/20\/three-quls-suffice\/","url_meta":{"origin":33307,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Quran: Three Quls suffice against every evil","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 20, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Khubayb reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cSpeak.\u201d I said, \u201cWhat should I say?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cSay, 'He is Allah, the One,' (112:1) and the two chapters of refuge, al-Falaq and al-Nas, every evening and morning three times. They will be\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3855,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/07\/27\/love-surah-ikhlaas-jannah\/","url_meta":{"origin":33307,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Quran: Love for Surat al-Ikhlas leads to Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 27, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: A man said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, I love this chapter, 'Say: He is Allah, the One,'\" (112:1). The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cYour love for it will admit\u00a0you into Paradise.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 774 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to\u00a0Al-Bukhari \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u064d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24898,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/05\/29\/dua-greatest-asma-al-husna\/","url_meta":{"origin":33307,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Dua: He asked Allah by His greatest name","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 29, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Buraydah al-Aslami reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, heard a man supplicating, saying, \u201cO Allah, I ask you by my testimony that you are Allah, there is no God but you, the One, the Eternal Refuge, who does not give birth and was not born, and to\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaeli